title: Man, 24, dies in Mosta traffic accident

text: Sunday, February 26, 2017, 17:58 Man, 24, dies in Mosta traffic accident Quad bike driver crashed into a bus, police said A 24-year-old Birżebbuġa man died this afternoon after crashing into a bus in Mosta, police have confirmed. The man was riding a quad bike down Vjal Millbrae when he somehow ended up driving into oncoming traffic at around 5.15pm. He was certified dead at the scene, police said.
